node.text:
I filmed this clip with @treyshotya back in 2017.

A oral history of how I got a chance to work with my favorite artist and how he and @jermainedupri changed my life and we shifted the culture by redefining the ballad. From his self titled album to My Way to 8701 to Confessions, my brother @usher has been the GOAT.

Happy 20th Anniversary to 8701.

LOVE YOU BOTH @USHER + @JERMAINEDUPRI.

node.text:
BURN.

Music is life. And we as creatives sacrifice much of our lives just to have moments like this. To see how the art we create affects people. This feeling never gets old and we are forever committed to making y’all feel this way as long as we can.

Thank you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bryan-Michael Cox on August 09, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person and beard.

node.text:
BIG CHUCK.

I always let you know how important you were to me and my development as a producer. I literally patterned my whole shit after you. There was always big love and respect for you. The most humble beast of a creative I knew. You will be sorely missed man.

This week has been un-fucking-real.

RIP Chucky Thompson @chucklife365, my hero.

Fellas,

BIG LOVE FOR MY NIGGAS.
@usher + @jermainedupri

Happy 20th Anniversary to 8701.
